/-- The surjective algebra morphism `R[X]/(minpoly R x) ‚Üí R[x]`.
If `R` is an integrally closed domain and `x` is integral, this is an isomorphism,
see `minpoly.equivAdjoin`. -/
def Minpoly.toAdjoin : AdjoinRoot (minpoly R x) ‚Üí‚Çê[R] adjoin R ({x} : Set S) :=
  liftAlgHom _ (Algebra.ofId R <| adjoin R {x}) ‚ü®x, self_mem_adjoin_singleton R x‚ü©
    (by change aeval _ _ = _; simp [‚Üê Subalgebra.coe_eq_zero, aeval_subalgebra_coe])

variable {R x}

